cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.CY 

The paper focuses on developing a computing system platform using artificial intelligence (AI) to support predictive situation awareness (PSAW) in the domain of infectious disease. The platform utilizes collective intelligence causal modeling and integrates multiple different data and models from independent researchers. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper also involves uncertainty treatment and decision making, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
